title: K.Flay Assortment (Other Material) v2
description:
Some old K.Flay solo songs, not from her Suburban Rap Queen or MASHed Potatoes albums. (I also have a lot of other K.Flay stuff in other torrents.)

Reupload of http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/6038687 - that was stuck at 98.5% because some pieces of the files had changed. The files didn't play as is, but I was able to load them into Audacity and re-export them.

The originals were 160kbps CBR. These are VBR equivalent to that. I removed silent fade-ins/fade-outs in some tracks, so the runtime of those is a bit shorter, but I left the audio otherwise unchanged. Is Anybody Listening.mp3 was renamed to Is There Anybody Listening.mp3 (the title tag was already accurate)
